  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >            <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915430/extras/619a5c68ad12b41546673df6aa8817e3.poster.avif?t=1773941005\" width=128 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915430/extras/619a5c68ad12b41546673df6aa8817e3.webm?t=1773941005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915430/extras/619a5c68ad12b41546673df6aa8817e3.poster.avif?t=1773941005\" width=128 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915430/extras/619a5c68ad12b41546673df6aa8817e3.webm?t=1773941005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915430/extras/619a5c68ad12b41546673df6aa8817e3.poster.avif?t=1773941005\" width=128 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915430/extras/619a5c68ad12b41546673df6aa8817e3.webm?t=1773941005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915430/extras/619a5c68ad12b41546673df6aa8817e3.poster.avif?t=1773941005\" width=128 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915430/extras/619a5c68ad12b41546673df6aa8817e3.webm?t=1773941005\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>✨ Idylls of the Lunar Maria is a match-3-inspired roguelite ✨</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle monsters and upgrade your powers with a unique combat system. Meet quirky characters along the way. Whimsical serendipity, mm.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915430/extras/1d0693e5dc55199140241dfc37328606.avif?t=1773941005\" width=616 height=300 /></span>Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ⚔️<strong> Fight enemies with a unique match-3-inspired gameplay</strong> - Match & merge tiles to attack, heal, defend, cast spells!  </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 👑<strong> Buy charms and upgrades</strong> to drastically change the game and defeat any foes you come across </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ✨<strong> Enjoy a variety of play-styles</strong> - Story mode, endless mode, even a rat mode!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐀 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✨ Tons of characters (222 currently!) to fight against (and with!) ✨</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915430/extras/02d352764722d6fef3960238ac9c1f59.avif?t=1773941005\" width=616 height=300 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build up attacks, defensive moves and special powers using the puzzle grid. Line up combos and strategise against your enemies' unique strategies and twists. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >✨ Every run is unique ✨</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make game-changing decisions along your journey. The game dynamically varies the types of characters, items and enemies you meet each run.  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1915430/extras/60f1f47935679ace95db6b8d3a1dca5f.avif?t=1773941005\" width=616 height=300 /></span></p>",
